  "instructions": [
    "Spread almond paste evenly onto center of ssam wrap, leaving a 1-inch border around the edges.",
    "Drizzle with 1 tablespoon of almond milk, followed by the crushed pine resin and cinnamon.",
    "Sprinkle sugar, if using, and walnuts over the filling, avoiding the border.",
    "Brush edges with egg wash and fold bottom edge of the wrap up over the filling.",
    "Fold in the sides and roll the wrap into a neat cylinder.",
    "Brush with egg wash and bake at 375°F (190°C) for 20 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Let cool for 5 minutes before serving."
  ],
